Super 👍 On peut donc enrichir la slide “Awareness” avec un deuxième point, ce qui rendra la section plus complète et cohérente.
Voici une version reformulée avec les deux initiatives :

⸻

👥 Awareness – Employee Engagement

Carbon Impact Indicators on Marketplace
A project is underway on the Marketplace, led by APEX, aiming to display indicators of carbon footprint impact based on employees’ usage of collaborative tools.

This initiative will:
	•	Raise awareness among employees about the environmental impact of their daily digital practices,
	•	Encourage the adoption of more sustainable behaviors by suggesting best practices,
	•	Provide transparency through data that we contribute to supply into the Marketplace.

Clean Data Week
We are also partnering with JC4E (Clean Company for Employees) for the Clean Data Week.
This initiative promotes:
	•	Best practices in sustainable IT,
	•	Awareness of the environmental impact of digital activities,
	•	Collective engagement of employees through dedicated campaigns and events.

⸻

👉 Là tu as une slide claire avec deux volets :
	1.	Individuel et quotidien via la Marketplace,
	2.	Collectif et événementiel via la Clean Data Week.

Veux-tu que je te propose un titre alternatif plus percutant que “Awareness – Employee Engagement”, par exemple “Raising Employee Awareness” ou “Sustainable IT Awareness” pour mieux refléter la dimension pédagogique ?
